2. METEOROLOGICAL SITUATION AT 1500: IRELAND LIES IN A SOUTHERLY AIRSTREAM
WHILE AN OCCLUDING FRONT APPROACHES THE WEST COAST A DEPRESSION FORMING
ON THE OCCLUSION WILL HALT ITS PROGRESS EASTWARDS TONIGHT AND THE DEPRESSION
ITSELF WILL SINK SLOWLY SOUTHWARDS AWAY FROM IRELAND DURING MONDAY.
